{"tid":1926401,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［意大利疫情］個半月間意大利報章訃聞由一版變十版","createTime":"2020-03-15T06:00:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-15T06:10:41.000Z","uid":39539,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4123c06ff0497c79307d5356729147c654a10656","tid":1926401,"uid":39539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T06:00:09.000Z","msg":"意大利的武漢肺炎疫情在一個多月間大爆發，截至周六逾2萬人確診，1,441人死，成為中國以外疫情最嚴重的國家，網上流傳一段片，顯示無情的病毒如何在意國殺人如麻。片段中，一名操意大利語男子翻閱意北疫情重災區倫巴第大區的《貝加莫報》（L&rsquo;Eco di Bergamo。貝加莫是倫巴第大區省分，在米蘭附近），先翻2月9日報內的訃聞版，佔了一版半，而當時意大利錄得僅3宗武漢肺炎病例<br />\n。接着片中男子翻閱上周五的《貝加莫報》，他翻了10版，全都是訃文，而當天全國錄得1.76萬宗確診，1,266宗死亡。意大利1月31日錄得該國首兩宗病例。兩名確診的中國旅客於1月23日抵達米蘭機場，隨後乘坐旅遊車前往羅馬。到上月21日，倫巴第大區爆發疫情，自此一發不可收拾，總理上周被迫宣佈「鎖國」抗疫<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BToURPD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBToURPD.png&h=708c8b76&s={SIZE}\" />。"},{"pid":"6da342633f41757f882c5ca7471f48d94cec8b43","tid":1926401,"uid":39539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T06:02:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VKXqYvf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVKXqYvf.png&h=78490dc5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"65c9622a0794e38df35fa630f6c2e4d89ab6edcd","tid":1926401,"uid":48195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T06:09:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/iQaQBqH0txs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FiQaQBqH0txs&d=%2BoN05yFcfnwTDzsdE0HOyUwFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=6780c63e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/iQaQBqH0txs</a><br />\n救樓主老母"},{"pid":"ce996ee268f56441c1d7de543f4f6e61f9e58f33","tid":1926401,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T06:10:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2565002/org/666d02d9e845feecbbb6be21c21e419f.jpg/lG-Bv21ZZNcaDg9vOPl9z0eyaUeWoZeHawwbNGsMGzQ?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/